author: Reuters Editorial
title: Macy's Says Plans To Open A Dedicated Backstage Distribution Center In Columbus, Ohio
text:
April 30, 2018 / 8:30 PM / Updated 2 minutes ago BRIEF-Macy's Says Plans To Open A Dedicated Backstage Distribution Center In Columbus, Ohio Reuters Staff
April 30 (Reuters) - Macy’s Inc:
* MACY’S INC - PLANS TO OPEN A DEDICATED BACKSTAGE DISTRIBUTION CENTER IN COLUMBUS, OHIO
* MACY’S INC - OPENING NEW BACKSTAGE DISTRIBUTION CENTER IN COLUMBUS, OHIO
* MACY’S INC - DISTRIBUTION CENTER IN COLUMBUS, OHIO IS PLANNED TO OPEN IN FALL 2019, ANTICIPATES IT WILL CREATE APPROXIMATELY 400 JOBS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: (Reuters.Briefs@thomsonreuters.com)
